column5: Had a late start today...about 9am...bite was very lite ....Meegs did greatagain but man did a miss lot of bites they were grabbing on the tube's skirt...had to work hard to get them on the hook and on the ice....anyhow fresh whities for dinner. Was wayyy too windy too....anything unsecured...was gooooone with the wind ha ha Shot from today:    Cheers, Ice Fisherman
great catch, you have caught more than me, good times
